name: Arialist
body:
### Introduction

This template suite for a blog, a personal homepage, and maybe journal site.

Current status of this project is **In Development**. Once, the template is ready we will notify on our [twitter](https://twitter.com/mentariworks).

### Usage

You can download the template code for development use. However, any usage on world wide web for any purpose require you to pay us for $8 for a single site license or $40 for developer license.

This template is licensed under MIT License.
